{
  "category": "Foundation — Fork Identity",
  "description": "Replace the opencode logo in packages/opencode/src/cli/logo.ts with protoLabs/Ava branding. Update UI color scheme in packages/opencode/src/cli/ui.ts. Replace all user-facing strings referencing 'opencode' with 'ava' or 'protoCli'. Update the welcome message and first-run dialog.\n\nIMPORTANT: Full design spec is in .automaker/context/ava-brand.md — read that file first before making any changes. It contains:\n- Exact replacement logo arrays for \"ava | cli\" using the existing _^~ glyph system\n- Exact ANSI color codes (violet-400 #a78bfa as primary, replacing cyan)\n- Complete Style object with updated TEXT_HIGHLIGHT/TEXT_INFO colors\n- Brand voice copy for welcome message and first-run dialog\n- String replacement table (opencode→ava, OpenCode→protoCli, etc.)\n- Scope discipline: only touch logo.ts, ui.ts, and user-facing strings\n\nFiles to modify:\n- packages/opencode/src/cli/logo.ts\n- packages/opencode/src/cli/ui.ts\n- packages/opencode/src/cli/cmd/tui/routes/home.tsx\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- TUI displays ava/protoLabs logo on startup (run bun run packages/opencode/src/index.ts to verify visually)\n- No 'opencode' text visible in the TUI\n- Color scheme reflects protoLabs brand (violet not cyan)",
